        <heading>2381.  Action by seizing creditor who has been compelled to reimburse purchaser</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2381.  Action by seizing creditor who has been compelled to reimburse purchaser
The seizing creditor may recover from his judgment debtor whatever he has had to pay to the purchaser who has been evicted.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
